name: Circus Ex Mortis
description: The New Moon Circus has come to Arkham, offering fun and wonder for all! But you are quickly thrown into the secrets and horrors behind the curtain! Unravel the mystery in this 8-scenario campaign with the help of 5 circus-themed investigators and nearly 400 player cards. Plus printable Moon and Tension tokens for use with the campaign and player expansion.
info: Tokens will be printed on normal cardstock, and are double-sided although we can’t guarantee alignment. By default you get two copies of each set so you could glue one image on each side of a cardboard circle. Moon Tokens require a 1" circle punch and Tension tokens a 1/2" punch or can be cut by hand.
